    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE YOUR FRIENDS' IMAGINATIONS</strong></h2>Traverse through vastly different worlds, battling your way through foes conjured up by your schoolmates. Explore Gracie’s fantastical mushroom castle or Ollie’s space pirate planet, tackling a variety of enemies, challenges, and games!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155270/extras/b977c78bc6098e52d706cf18430c1e1c.poster.avif?t=1740449316\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155270/extras/b977c78bc6098e52d706cf18430c1e1c.webm?t=1740449316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155270/extras/b977c78bc6098e52d706cf18430c1e1c.mp4?t=1740449316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BEFRIEND IMAGINATIVE ALLIES</strong></h2>Explore the school and converse with your schoolmates, getting to know them as you become friends. Exchange candy for ideas, providing powerful upgrades. Your schoolmates appear as bosses when you explore their worlds, and, once defeated, become playable characters! Unlock their unique abilities, narrative, and Ideas!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155270/extras/c5fba072ad1befbfc98e518649e1a2de.poster.avif?t=1740449316\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155270/extras/c5fba072ad1befbfc98e518649e1a2de.webm?t=1740449316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155270/extras/c5fba072ad1befbfc98e518649e1a2de.mp4?t=1740449316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UPGRADE YOUR ABILITIES</strong></h2>Many Ideas will come to you as you play, and you can give other kids sweets in exchange for their Ideas, too. Collect Ideas to upgrade your abilities, and create cool synergies by combining them. The more Ideas you have, the more powerful you become!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155270/extras/35474f2c47ae2a1f217a8b18e98104af.poster.avif?t=1740449316\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155270/extras/35474f2c47ae2a1f217a8b18e98104af.webm?t=1740449316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155270/extras/35474f2c47ae2a1f217a8b18e98104af.mp4?t=1740449316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
